                    .row
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-5
                            p
                                | I'm a front-end and back-end developer,
                                br
                                | living in San Francisco.
                        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-md-7
                            p I started coding when I was 15 and haven't stopped since. I love it, finding and implementing solutions to problems gives me a great thrill.

        script
